[SPEAKER_10]: Oh, okay, good.

43
00:03:53,231 --> 00:04:08,998
[SPEAKER_10]: Because what would be perfect would be just to put one on the pole and leave it and just so he can park on the pole and that will leave the room for the two people behind to be able to continue to park there because that's house beyond them.

44
00:04:09,578 --> 00:04:16,081
