54
00:04:58,198 --> 00:05:06,183
[SPEAKER_01]: The one other thing that we'd like to just make sure that you all are very aware of is that these are public handicap parking spots.

55
00:05:07,084 --> 00:05:12,628
[SPEAKER_01]: You may have in the past years, a long time ago, they used to actually put an assignment number on them.

56
00:05:12,988 --> 00:05:13,929
[SPEAKER_01]: We don't do that.

57
00:05:14,629 --> 00:05:15,850
[SPEAKER_01]: These are public spots.

58
00:05:16,290 --> 00:05:22,795
[SPEAKER_01]: If somebody else should be on his street and have a handicap placard, they could legally park there.

59
00:05:23,315 --> 00:05:26,838
[SPEAKER_01]: And you should just be aware of that, that it's not a reserved for him spots.

60
00:05:27,658 --> 00:05:28,878
[SPEAKER_10]: Okay, no, that's fine.

