00:09:20,152 --> 00:09:21,113
[SPEAKER_01]: Is that correct?

138
00:09:21,693 --> 00:09:26,736
[SPEAKER_01]: OK, and you've got a driveway that goes pretty far back and a space next to the house.

139
00:09:27,197 --> 00:09:33,861
[SPEAKER_01]: I'm very concerned when you say they block your driveway and won't move because in my mind that's a reason to call the police and tell them to come.

140
