[SPEAKER_01]: You know if they get tagged every day, they're going to stop doing it.

141
00:09:40,308 --> 00:09:47,631
[SPEAKER_01]: I know it's probably too early in the morning to call Medford parking, but blocking a driveway is not okay.

142
