150
00:10:49,127 --> 00:10:51,069
[SPEAKER_13]: And these people are just parking everywhere.

151
00:10:51,089 --> 00:10:58,353
[SPEAKER_13]: Even when you go there on a Friday night, a Saturday night, no matter what time it is, they park everywhere, all the way up Main Street.

152
00:10:59,093 --> 00:11:02,115
[SPEAKER_13]: So even if somebody comes to visit over there, there's no place to park.

153
00:11:05,894 --> 00:11:07,737
