00:11:12,105 --> 00:11:12,445
[SPEAKER_13]: Correct.

156
00:11:12,565 --> 00:11:16,873
[SPEAKER_13]: My mom has a handicap and so do I. I have a handicap plaque also.

157
00:11:16,893 --> 00:11:19,537
[SPEAKER_13]: So there's two handicapped people in the house.

158
00:11:20,285 --> 00:11:29,634
[SPEAKER_01]: And so you're aware, though, that if we put a handicap sign up, like I just said to the previous person, but for his case, who's going to park in front of his house with a handicap sign?

