799
01:04:47,507 --> 01:05:01,092
[SPEAKER_04]: The plan is to formally notify everyone that that's not going to be tolerated anymore, but we're offering the light green zones on this map as parking on the street, within the street,

800
01:05:02,624 --> 01:05:13,092
