[SPEAKER_04]: This emulates what exists at the next block down between Brogan and Tainter, and it's similar with the street.

802
01:05:22,240 --> 01:05:28,205
[SPEAKER_04]: The dark green indicates where parking regulation-wise is currently allowed,

803
01:05:29,297 --> 01:05:33,078
[SPEAKER_04]: The purple arrow shows where the parking on the sidewalk occurs.

804
01:05:34,138 --> 01:05:38,519
[SPEAKER_04]: The yellow is going to be no parking in the street or the sidewalk on that side.

805
01:05:39,099 --> 01:05:42,280
[SPEAKER_04]: The light green is parking in the street on that side.

806
01:05:43,880 --> 01:05:48,061
[SPEAKER_04]: So we're kicking folks off the sidewalk that shouldn't have been there in the first place.

