[SPEAKER_04]: This also shows the block from Tainter to Grogan, parking on both sides, similar curb to curb width, and all the cars are in the street, not on the sidewalk, and it works at least right now with the volume that exists.

825
01:07:21,925 --> 01:07:25,447
[SPEAKER_04]: So that's what we would be basically copying in this northern block.

826
01:07:25,827 --> 01:07:38,094
[SPEAKER_04]: But because of the lack of driveways on the park side, the ballpark side, we artificially created some gaps in the middle there to allow vehicles to pass one another.

827
