[SPEAKER_04]: That's what exists in this middle block right now.

828
01:07:41,096 --> 01:07:46,959
[SPEAKER_04]: It's tight, but because of driveways, people could pull over to the side and let each other by, two-way street.

829
01:07:47,931 --> 01:07:52,573
[SPEAKER_04]: But that only works up to a certain point, like Willis Ave and a previous traffic commission meeting.

830
01:07:53,253 --> 01:07:55,694
[SPEAKER_04]: That has so much volume that that doesn't work anymore.

831
01:07:55,714 --> 01:07:57,515
[SPEAKER_04]: So you do have to restrict parking on one side.

832
01:07:58,115 --> 01:08:02,537
[SPEAKER_04]: So we're willing to try this and then take it from there.

833
01:08:03,938 --> 01:08:06,699
[SPEAKER_04]: So the yellow arrows would be no parking in the street.

834
01:08:07,139 --> 01:08:09,740
[SPEAKER_04]: The light green arrow would be parking.

835
01:08:10,280 --> 01:08:13,902
[SPEAKER_04]: So this gives about seven spaces.

