[SPEAKER_04]: We can try it.

891
01:14:02,474 --> 01:14:14,564
[SPEAKER_04]: That was to allow for, instead of just an area at each end of the block to see a car coming and know to wait, it was given another opportunity to do that.

892
01:14:14,584 --> 01:14:17,987
[SPEAKER_04]: So it was an extra measure, but you could try that as well.

893
01:14:18,908 --> 01:14:23,209
