908
01:15:30,070 --> 01:15:30,891
[SPEAKER_06]: Do we know?

909
01:15:31,805 --> 01:15:40,067
[SPEAKER_04]: That we don't know, but it's basically the middle green, yellow, and green, and a little bit of the top yellow portion.

910
01:15:40,107 --> 01:15:45,988
[SPEAKER_04]: So it's probably 7, 8, 9, probably about 10 or 11 spaces.

911
01:15:48,389 --> 01:15:53,050
[SPEAKER_04]: Not that that's always a car there, 10 or 11, but lengthwise, it's 10 or 11 spaces.

912
01:15:54,130 --> 01:15:56,330
[SPEAKER_06]: Are any of the sidewalk panels broken or crumbled?

913
01:15:56,930 --> 01:15:57,271
[SPEAKER_06]: Yes.

914
01:15:58,891 --> 01:15:59,031
[SPEAKER_06]: Oof.

915
01:16:02,734 --> 01:16:03,034
[SPEAKER_05]: All right.

