[SPEAKER_16]: Steve, just for the record,

995
01:23:26,147 --> 01:23:31,631
[SPEAKER_16]: For years, since I've been in the early 80s, this was an extension of Hickey Park.

996
01:23:32,612 --> 01:23:34,093
[SPEAKER_16]: All right, it was a dirt area.

997
01:23:34,553 --> 01:23:36,475
[SPEAKER_16]: It was an extension of the park.

998
01:23:37,015 --> 01:23:41,138
[SPEAKER_16]: So people parked there, and they got hot topped at some point, and then

999
01:23:42,973 --> 01:23:51,597
[SPEAKER_16]: Um, so it became a sidewalk at some point, and there was still a debate whether it's an extension of the park or it was an actual sidewalk.

1000
01:23:52,077 --> 01:23:55,799
[SPEAKER_16]: And that's why the enforcement has gone back and forth since 1983.

1001
01:23:59,361 --> 01:24:01,702
