[SPEAKER_06]: Every now and then.

1010
01:24:23,546 --> 01:24:28,329
[SPEAKER_15]: And I do appreciate Todd's approach of like, let's do something and then continue to monitor it.

1011
01:24:28,429 --> 01:24:30,630
[SPEAKER_15]: So I do appreciate that.

