[SPEAKER_17]: The motion of Commissioner McGiven seconded by Commissioner Brzezinski for Park Street, Fellsbury West to Brogan Road, no parking any time, tow zone west side from Fellsbury West

1030
01:25:30,536 --> 01:25:39,981
