[SPEAKER_08]: We're a music school, so we do have multiple rooms.

1060
01:27:04,411 --> 01:27:07,272
[SPEAKER_08]: So you can see that long side there on Kenmare Road.

1061
01:27:08,012 --> 01:27:11,813
