[SPEAKER_08]: We have six to seven rooms that sometimes are running during the day.

1070
01:27:39,864 --> 01:27:45,511
[SPEAKER_08]: So that's six or seven employees and that's six to seven customers at any time.

1071
01:27:45,531 --> 01:27:51,397
[SPEAKER_08]: So we do have a couple spots here on Central Ave as well in front of the building too.

1072
01:27:52,018 --> 01:27:56,263
[SPEAKER_08]: So we were just trying to make more opportunities and options for customers

1073
01:27:57,063 --> 01:27:58,123
[SPEAKER_08]: closer to the buildings.

1074
01:27:58,163 --> 01:28:06,206
[SPEAKER_08]: We do try to tell our employees to park on the side streets as best as possible to make some of that off-street parking available.

1075
01:28:06,266 --> 01:28:20,250
[SPEAKER_08]: But like I said, even I was there on Saturday and I actually had to block the driveway for me to park, for me to get out to go in the building because sometimes it is very busy there if we have six or seven rooms running.

1076
01:28:22,162 --> 01:28:23,466
[SPEAKER_17]: Okay, thank you.

1077
01:28:25,292 --> 01:28:27,259
[SPEAKER_17]: Commissioners, questions of the petitioner?

