01:28:42,697 --> 01:28:48,124
[SPEAKER_01]: I guess my question is less of the petitioner and more for like toddlers.

1079
01:28:48,164 --> 01:28:51,428
[SPEAKER_01]: So the parking that is there now is unrestricted, right?

1080
01:28:51,628 --> 01:28:52,829
[SPEAKER_01]: Is it residential?

1081
01:28:53,964 --> 01:28:55,025
[SPEAKER_04]: So it's a good question.

1082
01:28:55,045 --> 01:29:06,034
[SPEAKER_04]: That's how I was raised my hand so that the business owner had reached out to us, Alvin and I asking what can be done because I believe she was aware of a potential petition for resident permit in this area.

1083
01:29:06,074 --> 01:29:08,656
[SPEAKER_04]: So wondering how is this going to impact her business.

1084
01:29:09,036 --> 01:29:14,841
[SPEAKER_04]: So we, I we highlight her that any resident permit would end next to the adjacent to the building.

1085
01:29:15,241 --> 01:29:19,664
