1086
01:29:20,565 --> 01:29:33,671
[SPEAKER_04]: patrons you know one hour or whatever it may be so it made sense for the business owner to come in here to ask for that knowing that the petition for resident permit parking may have come the same month which it didn't seem to but it's a good way.

