1176
01:35:18,903 --> 01:35:25,707
[SPEAKER_16]: I have been relentlessly down here tagging for the commercial violation ordinance.

1177
01:35:26,348 --> 01:35:32,352
[SPEAKER_16]: Unfortunately, Chief, that does not give me the right to tow these trucks.

1178
01:35:35,490 --> 01:35:43,957
[SPEAKER_16]: What these trucks are doing is they're parking their trucks there and their cars, and they go home at night.

1179
01:35:44,758 --> 01:35:48,561
[SPEAKER_16]: Then they come back in the morning, they leave their car, and they get in their rig and take off.

1180
01:35:50,302 --> 01:35:55,727
[SPEAKER_16]: Basically, they're parking on commercial streets for $25 a day, and that's the ticket.

1181
01:35:57,188 --> 01:36:02,372
[SPEAKER_16]: Again, it does not give me the right to tow, Chief, the commercial violence.

1182
01:36:04,168 --> 01:36:12,075
