1186
01:36:36,111 --> 01:36:49,981
[SPEAKER_14]: We were able to tow about 28 RVs, trailers, trucks, and so forth on January 1st of this year.

1187
01:36:51,823 --> 01:36:59,288
[SPEAKER_14]: And that's not even close to a number that we could have probably doubled that with the amount of trucks

1188
01:37:01,234 --> 01:37:15,879
