1189
01:37:16,039 --> 01:37:28,423
[SPEAKER_14]: But trailers, we're lucky enough that an unattended trailer is a ordinance throughout the state that no unattended trailer can be parked on any street at any location for any period of time.

1190
01:37:29,570 --> 01:37:32,652
[SPEAKER_14]: When we have seen those, we've been lucky enough that we've been able to get those off.

1191
